        How Rental Yield Affects Sale Price for Brisbane Investment Properties
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        What yield figures actually do to your sale price, how below-market rent can hurt investor appeal, and when waiting for a lease to end is worth it.
      </p>
